parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: SRS Light Illumination and Airbag System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to a lack of deployment in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or fatality. The illumination of the SRS light can indicate a faulty airbag system, which can lead to a false sense of security and compromise vehicle safety.
symptoms: SRS light remains on
passenger side airbag visible or protruding
airbag failure to deploy in the event of an accident.

airbag failure to deploy in the event of an accident.
